data.title: Tribute to icon AMY WINEHOUSE
data.meta_description: “Mia Karter is magnificent…visually stunning and musically moving…” Audience favorites THE WINEHOUSE EXPERIENCE featuring, singer Mia Karter, pay musical tribute to Grammy Award-winning singer Amy Winehouse who’s distinctively warm vocals, soulful songwriting and signature style made her a beloved world-renowned icon. Only at Catalina Jazz Club, Hollywood. Backed by a 9-piece ensemble complete with Amy’s signature horn-section and choreographed …
